body: Latino voters in swing states like Nevada could decide the outcome of the 2016 race for president. Democrats have historically had a lock on their vote. Republicans think they have a formula to change that.

title: Nevada GOP Aggressively Tries To Break Democrats' Lock On Latino Voters
